{"word":"μέτοχος","slug":"μέτοχος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μέτοχος</b></el> <el>(μέτοχος, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μετέχω'><el>μετέχω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>sharing in, partaking of</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a> <i>a partner, accomplice in</i>, <el>τοῦ φόνου</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}